						<summary>

						<p>On a hero-stone lying in the Hanumantadēva temple.</p>						

						<p>1370-71 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1292, Sunday, the other details being lost. The Śaka year corresponds to 1370-71 A.D.</p>						

						<p>States that the memorial stone marks the spot where a warrior fought and died. The name of the hero and other details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
